## ğŸ“‚ API Endpoints

### 1. Login
`POST /login`

**Request Body**
```json
{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "pass123"
}
Response

json
Copy code
{
  "message": "Login successful",
  "token": "randomGeneratedToken"
}
2. Search
GET /search?token=<authToken>&q=laptop

Returns a list of matching products.

3. Cart
POST /cart

Request Body

json
Copy code
{
  "token": "<authToken>",
  "productId": 1
}
4. Logout
POST /logout

Request Body

json
Copy code
{
  "token": "<authToken>"
}
